thread.title: BRIEF-Pharming Announces FDA Acceptance For Review Of Supplemental Biologics License Application

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Pharming Announces FDA Acceptance For Review Of Supplemental Biologics License Application

organizations.name: fda acceptance for review of supplemental biologics

text:
Jan 17 (Reuters) - PHARMING GROUP NV:
* PHARMING ANNOUNCES FDA ACCEPTANCE FOR REVIEW OF SUPPLEMENTAL BIOLOGICS LICENSE APPLICATION FOR RUCONEST® FOR PROPHYLAXIS OF HEREDITARY ANGIOEDEMA ATTACKS
* ‍FDA INDICATED SBLA IS SUFFICIENTLY COMPLETE TO PERMIT SUBSTANTIVE REVIEW
* ‍FDA SET AN ACTION DATE OF SEPTEMBER 21, 2018​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
